# Relume.io Site Builder Prompt – Cloud Data Consulting

Company Overview  
Cloud Data Consulting builds AI‑ready data architecture for $50M–$500M firms. Our D.A.T.A.S. framework (Diagnose, Analyze, Transform, Accelerate, Scale) turns AI ambition into reality. Core message: “Your AI strategy depends on your data strategy.”

Target Audience  
• C‑suite (CDO/CTO/CIO) in healthcare, finance, manufacturing, retail  
• Data‑engineering & BI leaders adopting Snowflake

Tone & Messaging  
Voice: authoritative, business‑centric.  
Tone: confident, strategic, outcome‑driven.  
Avoid jargon; highlight ROI and partnership.

Key Messages  
1. AI success demands a solid data foundation.  
2. Proven D.A.T.A.S. methodology delivers results fast.  
3. We bridge business vision and technical execution—beyond Big 4 slideware.

Priority CTAs  
1. Get AI Readiness Score 2. Schedule Consultation 3. View Case Studies 4. Download Guide

Site Map & Essential Content  

**1 Homepage**  
• Hero: “Your AI Strategy Depends on Your Data Strategy”  
  Sub: “Only 13 % of companies are AI‑ready—join them.”  
  CTAs: Get Score | See Methodology  
  Trust: 125+ yrs expertise, 19 Snowflake launches  
• Pain: Why 75 % of AI projects fail (silos, legacy tech, weak governance)  
• Solution: D.A.T.A.S. snapshot (5 steps, 30‑day quick wins)  
• Proof: quantified client wins → CTA “Start Your Transformation”

**2 Services (index + four detail pages)**  
A. AI Readiness Assessment  $35k | 2 wks – 6‑dimension score, benchmark, roadmap (“Most score < 30 %”)  
B. AI‑Ready Platform  $150–350k | 3–6 mo – Snowflake + dbt stack, governance, ML prep  
C. DW Modernization  $100–250k | 2–4 mo – cloud migration, optimization, cost reduction  
D. Strategic AI Enablement  $200k+ | 6–12 mo – enterprise data strategy, change mgmt

**3 About**  
Mission, leadership bios, Snowflake partnership badges, “We implement strategy, not just recommend.”

**4 Resources / Blog**  
Guides (“Hidden Cost of Bad Data”), ROI calculator, industry AI readiness checklists, Snowflake tips.

**5 Contact**  
HubSpot form with qualifier Qs, “Schedule Consultation,” map, team photos.

Wireframe Hints  
• Sticky top nav with CTA button.  
• Fold‑one hero, fold‑two pain, fold‑three solution, fold‑four proof/CTA.  
• Services index uses card grid; each card clicks to detail page template (hero, benefits, process, testimonial, CTA).  
• Resource hub uses filterable masonry.  
• Contact page split: form (left 60 %), brand imagery (right 40 %).

Design & Brand  
Style: enterprise‑grade, clean, modern.  
Palette: blue primary (#204C8C), orange accent (#F36E21) or green (#3AB54A), neutral grays/white.  
Visuals: data‑viz motifs, subtle tech texture, original photography.  
Components: hero, process flow, stat counters, testimonial carousel, ROI calculator embed, HubSpot forms, badge strip.

Technical & SEO  
• HubSpot integration for all forms.  
• Load speed <= 2 s; WebCore vitals green.  
• Schema markup: Organization, Service, FAQ.  
• Keywords: “AI readiness,” “data strategy consulting,” “Snowflake consulting,” plus vertical modifiers.  
• Accessible (WCAG 2.1 AA).

Deliverables to Relume AI  
✓ Generate full sitemap above  
✓ Produce wireframes per section notes  
✓ Apply design system (palette, typography, spacing)  
✓ Output page copy blocks with CTA microcopy

Result: a professional, high‑converting B2B site that positions Cloud Data Consulting as the indispensable bridge between enterprise AI ambition and technical reality.